WEBVTT

01:28.839 --> 01:30.007
<i>Mommy!</i>

01:30.174 --> 01:32.593
AT THE END OF THE TUNNEL

01:32.760 --> 01:33.803
<i>Mommy!</i>

01:33.969 --> 01:36.514
<i>- What?
- I'm with Casimiro!</i>

01:45.189 --> 01:47.108
<i>Lunch is ready!</i>

01:47.900 --> 01:50.069
<i>I'm on the slide!</i>

02:05.584 --> 02:07.503
<i>I like Mathematics.</i>

02:07.670 --> 02:09.255
<i>You'll have to work hard.</i>

02:09.421 --> 02:12.299
<i>If I do it wrong,
PH get a zero.</i>

02:12.466 --> 02:14.677
<i>No, you won't get a zero.</i>

02:17.555 --> 02:18.889
<i>Sweetie, time for bed.</i>

02:19.056 --> 02:21.392
<i>Wait, let me tuck in Casimiro.</i>

02:21.559 --> 02:24.061
<i>Come on, go to bed.
It's late, sweetheart.</i>

03:43.849 --> 03:45.392
Pick up, damn it!

03:47.102 --> 03:50.606
Yes, I'm calling for Casimiro's
test results.

03:51.482 --> 03:52.608
Joaquin.

03:53.609 --> 03:58.197
No, my name is Joaquin.
Casimiro is my dog.

03:59.073 --> 04:02.618
Yeah, he's very old.
He doesn't want to walk anymore.

04:05.329 --> 04:09.208
Well, is there any type
of treatment

04:09.375 --> 04:11.669
or operation that can be done?

04:14.255 --> 04:15.673
But it wouldn't solve anything.

04:17.841 --> 04:21.053
Okay, thank you.
I'm going to think about it.

04:26.725 --> 04:29.061
HOW TO PUT A DOG TO SLEEP
WITHOUT PAIN

05:03.887 --> 05:05.472
- Hi.
- Hi.

05:05.639 --> 05:07.016
Did you put an ad
renting

05:07.182 --> 05:08.350
a room with a terrace?

05:08.767 --> 05:10.311
Can we see it?

05:11.061 --> 05:13.772
Yes, but you should have called
before coming.

05:14.648 --> 05:15.774
Come on, Betty.

05:19.320 --> 05:22.448
It's up there.

05:23.907 --> 05:25.784
- How cute! What's its name?
- Casimiro.

05:25.951 --> 05:26.660
Don't touch him!

05:26.827 --> 05:29.580
He doesn't like people
he doesn't know.

05:30.164 --> 05:31.623
Do you live alone?

05:32.082 --> 05:33.042
Yes.

05:34.793 --> 05:38.255
I don't think this is what
you're looking for.

05:39.214 --> 05:40.424
It's not the ideal place...

05:40.591 --> 05:42.384
How do you know
what I'm looking for?

05:43.677 --> 05:45.387
- Go up and look at it.
- Okay.

05:45.679 --> 05:49.516
The door to the terrace
is next to the bathroom door.

05:49.683 --> 05:51.226
Okay.

06:13.290 --> 06:15.459
Can we move in today?

06:16.502 --> 06:17.294
What?

06:17.461 --> 06:20.339
My stuff is nearby,
I can bring it right over.

06:20.506 --> 06:21.840
You'd be saving us
if you say yes.

06:22.007 --> 06:24.635
- No, no...
- Here's what we'll do.

06:24.802 --> 06:26.929
Don't say anything.
We'll be back in half an hour.

06:27.096 --> 06:29.681
- Call me first.
- Don't show it to anyone.

06:29.848 --> 06:30.891
Please, call me first.

06:31.058 --> 06:32.434
- Half an hour.
- Thanks.

06:33.268 --> 06:34.395
Thanks!

06:47.282 --> 06:48.826
Come in, come in.

06:49.201 --> 06:50.494
Thanks.

07:14.935 --> 07:16.019
This one?

07:17.980 --> 07:19.148
There.

07:20.816 --> 07:22.776
Shouldn't it go over here?

07:23.694 --> 07:25.154
Just asking.

07:27.406 --> 07:30.409
I don't need company.

07:30.993 --> 07:34.079
That's not why I rented the room,
to have someone organizing

07:34.246 --> 07:35.664
and cleaning the house.

07:35.831 --> 07:37.040
What bullshit.

07:47.593 --> 07:50.012
What are these marks
on the door?

07:52.347 --> 07:53.432
The marks...

07:53.599 --> 07:55.476
When you're growing,
as you get taller...

08:03.734 --> 08:06.653
How many lighters
do you use a day?

08:07.070 --> 08:09.198
I'm only thinking of Betty...

08:11.533 --> 08:14.119
Betty, the little girl
who's always with me.

08:15.871 --> 08:19.458
Since you asked, I'll tell you.
I'm a dancer.

08:19.625 --> 08:22.753
That's what I do.
I dance in a club.

08:22.920 --> 08:24.171
I'm a stripper.

08:24.338 --> 08:25.422
But not the kind you're thinking.

08:25.714 --> 08:27.257
That wouldn't be my problem.

08:40.771 --> 08:42.648
FORECLOSURE
FINAL NOTICE

09:00.582 --> 09:03.669
Can you turn down the music
a little, please?

09:07.422 --> 09:08.298
Excuse me.

09:09.091 --> 09:10.717
Have you seen my daughter?

09:10.884 --> 09:11.843
No.

09:12.010 --> 09:14.471
- Could she have gone back there?
- No.

09:14.638 --> 09:16.223
She couldn't have gone
back there.

09:16.390 --> 09:17.516
Don't go back there.

09:17.683 --> 09:20.310
She could have walked right by you
and you didn't see her.

09:20.477 --> 09:21.603
Damn it. Betty!

09:25.941 --> 09:27.693
Sweetie, are you out here?

09:27.985 --> 09:29.152
Betty!

09:34.825 --> 09:36.159
Betty!

09:40.706 --> 09:42.291
Are you here?

10:00.267 --> 10:01.643
Betty!

10:06.106 --> 10:07.608
Betty!

10:10.027 --> 10:12.154
She likes to hide,
I don't know why.

10:12.321 --> 10:13.864
She suddenly disappears.

10:14.031 --> 10:16.408
That's locked, she couldn't have
gone in there.

10:16.575 --> 10:19.244
- Did you check the bedroom?
- Yes, I did.

10:19.411 --> 10:20.662
Betty!

10:21.872 --> 10:23.081
Betty!

10:30.130 --> 10:31.506
Sweetheart!

10:32.257 --> 10:33.258
Come here.

10:33.759 --> 10:36.261
Hide in easier places to find!

10:36.470 --> 10:38.680
Here, let me see your pockets.

10:39.931 --> 10:42.267
I'll put this back where it goes.

11:43.370 --> 11:45.997
Hey, how long has it been
since you saw the terrace?

11:46.873 --> 11:48.709
You know what's out there?

11:49.334 --> 11:50.877
Obviously not.

11:52.087 --> 11:55.048
I can't describe it.
You have to come up and see it.

11:55.507 --> 11:58.051
Yeah, I'd love to go skating too.

11:59.511 --> 12:00.637
Come on.

12:13.108 --> 12:15.318
In the contract
you made me sign...

12:16.027 --> 12:20.115
I saw that today happens to be
your birthday.

12:28.331 --> 12:30.625
You don't like kids?

12:31.543 --> 12:33.336
You don't talk to her,
you barely look at her...

12:33.503 --> 12:35.046
She doesn't talk to me
either.

12:35.213 --> 12:37.799
She doesn't talk to anyone,
not even me.

12:38.091 --> 12:39.134
She's not mute.

12:39.301 --> 12:41.303
She just stopped talking.

12:42.554 --> 12:45.307
The psychologist said it was better
not to pressure her.

12:48.059 --> 12:50.228
Who do you spend
Christmas and New Year's with?

12:50.395 --> 12:51.313
With Casimiro.

12:52.606 --> 12:54.065
That's great.

12:54.232 --> 12:56.276
There will be 4 of us now.

12:59.404 --> 13:00.614
Were you always like this?

13:01.323 --> 13:03.116
Like what?

13:07.746 --> 13:10.665
Shall I take her to bed
and open another bottle?

13:12.209 --> 13:13.752
Come on, sweetie.

13:13.919 --> 13:14.961
Let's go.

13:27.098 --> 13:29.142
I like to dance, but really dance.

13:29.684 --> 13:30.894
You know?

13:31.102 --> 13:33.021
I studied dance.

13:33.688 --> 13:36.900
After that, I came to Buenos Aires,
and...

13:43.448 --> 13:46.117
My old man's house
was full of books too.

13:47.244 --> 13:49.204
There were books everywhere.

13:52.082 --> 13:53.917
You don't care at all,
do you?

13:54.292 --> 13:55.627
I'm listening.

13:55.794 --> 13:59.339
If all you need is money,
why don't you sell this huge house?

14:01.883 --> 14:03.760
This is my home.

14:04.219 --> 14:07.138
Yeah, but this house
must be worth 600,000 dollars.

14:07.347 --> 14:08.223
At least.

14:11.768 --> 14:15.146
What a shitty birthday.

14:15.814 --> 14:18.024
I wish I could dance, but...

14:23.238 --> 14:24.281
Okay.

14:28.159 --> 14:29.411
What are you doing?

14:29.703 --> 14:31.413
It's what I do best.

14:32.789 --> 14:33.832
Here?

14:33.999 --> 14:35.917
Tomorrow we'll just say
it was the booze.

14:36.084 --> 14:37.752
But no laughing

14:37.919 --> 14:39.504
or teasing me about it.

16:42.752 --> 16:44.671
No, Joaquin said not to!

16:45.130 --> 16:47.424
Betty, that's enough!
I won't say it again!

19:34.174 --> 19:35.925
<i>Tell those two to stop
in there.</i>

19:38.887 --> 19:40.763
<i>I heard something
at the cripple's place.</i>

19:40.930 --> 19:42.265
<i>I didn't hear shit.</i>

19:42.432 --> 19:45.643
<i>I said I heard something,
you dumbshit.</i>

19:47.061 --> 19:48.897
<i>It was the elevator.
Lefty, should I take this?</i>

19:49.480 --> 19:51.399
<i>Let me listen.
Keep quiet.</i>

19:53.151 --> 19:55.445
<i>We should have plastered
on this wall.</i>

20:01.826 --> 20:03.036
<i>I don't hear anything.</i>

20:03.995 --> 20:05.496
<i>Tell those two come out.</i>

20:05.663 --> 20:06.998
<i>Stay here and listen.</i>

20:11.169 --> 20:13.004
<i>Let's all go back up.</i>

20:19.385 --> 20:21.221
What are you doing?
Come up here!

20:22.472 --> 20:25.225
Don't miss this!
Your dog mummy woke up!

20:25.683 --> 20:27.518
Don't be so insensitive!

20:27.685 --> 20:29.646
- Come up here!
- I'm coming.

20:30.897 --> 20:31.731
Come up!

21:07.809 --> 21:08.810
He got up.

21:09.143 --> 21:10.603
And he stood there
for a while.

21:12.188 --> 21:13.856
Aren't you happy?

21:14.023 --> 21:15.900
Yeah, can't you tell?

21:16.401 --> 21:18.778
Is something wrong?
You look like shit.

21:19.612 --> 21:21.948
No, I'm fine.
What is this?

21:22.115 --> 21:25.451
This is that I'm not going
to let you keep working.

21:25.618 --> 21:29.038
We'll cook and eat together
to celebrate Casimiro's revival.

21:29.247 --> 21:34.043
I might not do a striptease
for you tonight...

22:20.840 --> 22:24.886
<i>I heard the cripple's elevator
10 minutes ago.</i>

22:25.053 --> 22:25.887
<i>What do we do?</i>

22:26.054 --> 22:28.973
<i>I checked, we're good.
Let's keep going.</i>

22:39.901 --> 22:41.152
<i>Come on,
we need to hurry up.</i>

22:41.319 --> 22:43.112
<i>How are things going in there,
Puppet?</i>

22:43.279 --> 22:44.864
<i>- Hot but okay.
- Puppet?</i>

22:45.907 --> 22:47.325
PUPPET

22:47.492 --> 22:50.495
<i>- What am I, your servant?
- Why are you asking about the heat?</i>

22:50.661 --> 22:52.455
<i>- Pichi, Pichi.
- What?</i>

22:52.622 --> 22:54.832
<i>- Put that over there.
- Yes, sir, but...</i>

22:54.999 --> 22:56.751
<i>We have to be more careful,
Papito.</i>

22:56.918 --> 22:58.586
<i>Keep going,
quit screwing around.</i>

22:58.753 --> 23:01.547
<i>One... second,
let me... turn on... the light.</i>

23:01.714 --> 23:03.174
<i>How are we for 10 days?</i>

23:03.341 --> 23:04.801
<i>Okay, I think.</i>

23:10.098 --> 23:11.349
SATURDAY DECEMBER 24TH

23:11.516 --> 23:13.184
<i>These beams are no good.</i>

23:13.351 --> 23:14.769
<i>Take them upstairs,
they're in the way.</i>

23:15.478 --> 23:16.687
BEAMS?

23:16.896 --> 23:18.606
<i>Mr. Galereto,
should I take this up too?</i>

23:18.773 --> 23:19.899
<i>No, leave it for now.</i>

23:20.066 --> 23:21.359
<i>I'm going up to sleep
for a while.</i>

23:21.526 --> 23:23.111
<i>I'll tell René to come down.</i>

23:23.277 --> 23:25.446
<i>Canario, I'm taking this
to the table.</i>

23:25.613 --> 23:27.407
<i>Whose glass is this?</i>

23:29.075 --> 23:30.827
<i>Pass it over here.</i>

23:32.078 --> 23:33.371
<i>Should we stop at 6?</i>

23:33.538 --> 23:35.706
<i>Yeah, we'll see how it was.</i>

24:23.713 --> 24:25.798
You can't do this to me now.

24:26.174 --> 24:28.551
We signed a contract,
you asked me a ton of questions.

24:28.718 --> 24:30.094
We did sign a contract.

24:30.261 --> 24:32.180
You don't trust me?
ls there a reason?

24:32.346 --> 24:37.185
It has nothing to do with trust.
I just need a couple of weeks...

24:37.351 --> 24:39.270
Why do we have to find
somewhere else right away?

24:39.437 --> 24:41.647
I can't explain why, okay?

24:41.814 --> 24:44.358
- Just give me a few days...
-l'll explain it.

24:45.401 --> 24:47.820
You're scared because
we're getting closer.

24:47.987 --> 24:50.406
Because the other night...
I danced for you.

24:51.657 --> 24:53.409
That has nothing to do with it.

24:53.993 --> 24:55.786
I saw how you look at me.

24:56.412 --> 24:59.248
And you think less of yourself
because of that wheelchair.

24:59.415 --> 25:01.417
You were comfortable
by yourself

25:01.584 --> 25:03.711
and you're scared of losing that.

25:05.171 --> 25:07.215
You're smart, Joaquin
and good-looking

25:07.381 --> 25:10.718
but your life is awful and you
want to keep it that way.

25:13.554 --> 25:15.431
I know you like me.

25:16.766 --> 25:19.685
And you have no idea what I'm
going through and that scares you.

25:23.648 --> 25:25.024
Think it over.

25:25.191 --> 25:27.818
Tomorrow you can tell me
if you want us to leave.

25:27.985 --> 25:30.613
But give it one more day,
please.

25:41.624 --> 25:46.087
THEY WORK ONLY AT NIGHT

25:52.635 --> 25:55.888
THEY CARRY DIRT UPSTAIRS IN BAGS

26:00.643 --> 26:03.437
WHAT ARE THE BEAMS FOR?

26:18.035 --> 26:19.078
Hi.

26:19.495 --> 26:20.830
Good morning.

26:21.956 --> 26:22.915
Want some coffee?

26:23.082 --> 26:24.083
Yeah.

26:28.629 --> 26:29.922
Thanks.

26:32.675 --> 26:34.635
I'm going downstairs to work.

26:37.138 --> 26:38.639
I thought it over.

26:38.973 --> 26:41.726
And... I don't want you to leave.

26:43.436 --> 26:44.312
That's it.

26:50.610 --> 26:52.486
Come down when you can.

26:52.653 --> 26:55.406
I want to show you something
you won't believe.

27:11.922 --> 27:15.635
<i>Schwarzenegger, Schwarzenegger,
when can we eat something?</i>

27:16.052 --> 27:18.054
<i>You want to stop... and eat?</i>

27:18.220 --> 27:20.514
<i>You're lazy even...
even with millions at stake.</i>

27:21.557 --> 27:24.226
<i>This heat is unbearable.
Can't we do something?</i>

27:24.393 --> 27:29.440
<i>Yeah, right. I'll install
some air conditioning later.</i>

27:45.206 --> 27:48.250
<i>It's not silly, according to
our natal charts, it's better to do it</i>

27:48.417 --> 27:50.086
<i>the 25th than the 24th.
I'm only asking for one more day.</i>

27:50.252 --> 27:53.923
<i>Know what the horoscope said about
1/12th of the passengers on the Titanic?</i>

27:54.090 --> 27:57.051
<i>"ldeal day for a trip."</i>

27:57.218 --> 27:59.053
<i>We should do it on the 25th,
not the 24th.</i>

27:59.261 --> 28:01.347
<i>- Trust me.
- Yeah, yeah.</i>

28:02.181 --> 28:04.141
<i>Lefty, show me.</i>

28:06.644 --> 28:08.938
<i>- I'm even trying to help...
- Look.</i>

28:09.146 --> 28:10.898
<i>Will it be strong enough?</i>

28:11.065 --> 28:12.274
<i>Yeah, I guess.</i>

28:12.441 --> 28:14.902
<i>I don't know how it works in Spain,
but don't say I guess.</i>

28:15.528 --> 28:17.154
<i>Don't worry, it'll be fine.</i>

28:18.906 --> 28:20.908
<i>Did you set the detonator,
Canario?</i>

28:21.075 --> 28:22.076
<i>Almost, almost.</i>

28:22.410 --> 28:24.203
<i>But this is harder
than baptizing a cat.</i>

28:24.370 --> 28:26.956
<i>"Almost, almost."</i>

28:27.123 --> 28:29.208
<i>Galereto, you have a visitor.</i>

28:30.793 --> 28:33.963
<i>- What is she doing here?
- Should we leave you alone?</i>

28:36.549 --> 28:37.925
<i>What happened?</i>

28:38.509 --> 28:40.469
<i>I came over the terrace.</i>

28:40.845 --> 28:42.430
<i>Yeah, but what happened?</i>

28:42.596 --> 28:45.808
<i>He changed his mind.
He said to move out.</i>

28:52.189 --> 28:54.734
<i>- Did he go back down after 8'?
- No.</i>

28:55.025 --> 28:56.610
You're sure he can't hear
anything?

28:56.777 --> 28:59.488
He can't hear anything, Javi.
From anywhere.

29:00.698 --> 29:02.366
Keep stalling.

29:02.533 --> 29:06.120
Tell him you'll look
and can't find anything.

29:06.370 --> 29:08.080
Keep him occupied.

29:10.040 --> 29:11.333
Look what I got you.

29:13.836 --> 29:17.465
- Besides the crap you buy me...
- Crap?

29:17.631 --> 29:19.341
Stop groping me.

29:20.050 --> 29:22.178
You don't give a shit
what happens to me.

29:22.344 --> 29:24.430
You leave me with another guy

29:24.597 --> 29:26.474
-and you don't give a fuck.
- He's a cripple.

29:27.391 --> 29:30.936
<i>Or I wouldn't have gotten you into this.
You know Pm crazy about you.</i>

29:31.103 --> 29:34.315
- I wish I believed you.
- What's wrong, baby?

29:34.815 --> 29:35.900
Of course I am.

29:39.361 --> 29:41.030
<i>You're making me horny.</i>

29:41.197 --> 29:43.699
Go on, I have to keep working.
Listen.

29:44.283 --> 29:45.785
No matter what happens,

29:45.951 --> 29:48.537
don't come back here.
It was dangerous.

29:48.704 --> 29:50.080
Message, nothing else.

29:50.498 --> 29:52.374
I'm serious, baby.

29:58.672 --> 30:00.382
Can I come down?

30:02.092 --> 30:02.968
What?

30:03.219 --> 30:04.220
Can I come down?

30:07.431 --> 30:08.599
<i>I'll</i> be right up.

30:10.059 --> 30:11.560
You weren't going to show me
something?

30:18.692 --> 30:20.027
Is something wrong?

30:25.616 --> 30:27.827
Yeah, I wanted to show you...

30:27.993 --> 30:31.080
something on YouTube.
ls your daughter up there?

30:31.705 --> 30:33.541
- Yeah.
- Okay, I'll be right up.

30:37.878 --> 30:39.129
Okay.

32:26.487 --> 32:28.614
Sweetie, those felt pens
stain everything.

32:28.781 --> 32:31.492
Look at your hands.

32:34.203 --> 32:35.704
Okay, let's see.

32:36.163 --> 32:39.959
Cream cheese, sweet potato jelly,
toothpaste, wine, soap,

32:40.167 --> 32:42.461
rice, cookies, mayonnaise.
Anything else?

32:42.670 --> 32:43.879
Nothing else.

32:45.130 --> 32:47.758
Don't worry, she won't go anywhere.
I think.

32:47.925 --> 32:49.885
Bye, sweetie!

32:56.141 --> 32:58.644
What you're drawing
is very pretty.

33:01.689 --> 33:03.732
It's beautiful, what is it?

33:06.860 --> 33:08.320
Very pretty.

33:10.990 --> 33:12.533
That's a nice color.

33:13.617 --> 33:15.869
You don't want to tell me
what it is?

33:19.873 --> 33:21.750
Tell me when you finish it.

33:25.254 --> 33:27.047
Bye, Casimiro.

33:57.119 --> 34:00.748
<i>- These pipes move a lot.
- They need a brace.</i>

34:00.914 --> 34:03.500
<i>Maybe we should find something
bigger.</i>

34:03.667 --> 34:05.711
<i>Then we can get more
out of each trip.</i>

34:05.878 --> 34:07.546
<i>Yeah.</i>

34:08.464 --> 34:11.383
<i>Look what I found
in Puppet's things.</i>

34:12.509 --> 34:14.053
<i>Where was it?</i>

34:14.219 --> 34:16.305
<i>In the pocket of his backpack.</i>

34:16.638 --> 34:18.724
<i>He sent the last message</i>

34:18.891 --> 34:21.143
<i>at 11 P.M.
He's asleep now.</i>

34:22.352 --> 34:24.646
<i>Get Puppet over here.</i>

34:25.731 --> 34:28.192
