1:05:13.911 --> 1:05:15.913
No, please.

1:05:16.079 --> 1:05:18.415
Let me keep listening.
Please.

1:05:18.582 --> 1:05:19.917
Please.

1:05:20.584 --> 1:05:23.754
You said she was 4
when she stopped talking.

1:05:23.921 --> 1:05:24.755
Yes.

1:05:24.922 --> 1:05:27.007
How old is she now, 6?

1:05:27.674 --> 1:05:28.842
Two years?

