wants you to do these things.</i>

1:05:47.235 --> 1:05:49.655
<i>We're going to play a game.</i>

1:05:50.906 --> 1:05:53.533
<i>But we can't tell Mommy.</i>

1:05:54.493 --> 1:05:57.245
<i>Mommy will be jealous
if we tell her.</i>

1:05:58.664 --> 1:06:02.000
<i>Boys and girls always play
like this.</i>

1:06:02.960 --> 1:06:05.087
<i>Come here, little one.</i>

1:06:06.505 --> 1:06:08.423
<i>Don't be afraid, Casimiro.</i>

1:06:08.590 --> 1:06:09.216
No, no!

1:06:09.383 --> 1:06:10.759
<i>It's okay.</i>

1:06:10.968 --> 1:06:13.845
No,no,no!

1:06:20.185 --> 1:06:22.354
No, please!

1:06:22.688 --> 1:06:24.564
She's okay now, she's okay.

1:06:24.731 --> 1:06:26.942
She's playing with some toys
I gave her.

1:06:27.150 --> 1:06:30.570
That son of a bitch!
That son of a bitch!

1:06:31.196 --> 1:06:34.616
Now that we know,
we can help her.

1:06:37.327 --> 1:06:39.788
