1:06:48.755 --> 1:06:51.550
I can ruin his life.

1:06:51.717 --> 1:06:54.553
I'm going to kill him!
I'm going to kill him!

1:06:54.720 --> 1:06:58.515
Calm down.
I need you to calm down.

1:07:00.726 --> 1:07:03.979
Think about what's happening.

1:07:05.480 --> 1:07:06.565
And help me.

1:07:06.732 --> 1:07:08.483
What do you want me to do?

1:07:09.109 --> 1:07:11.069
Call him, talk to him.

1:07:11.236 --> 1:07:13.030
Tell him everything is fine.

1:07:13.196 --> 1:07:16.033
That everything is fine.
Not to worry.

1:07:16.616 --> 1:07:18.869
Tell him everything's fine.

1:07:19.828 --> 1:07:22.414
He's calling you.
Talk to him.

1:07:25.083 --> 1:07:26.501
Hi.

1:07:27.627 --> 1:07:30.380
<i>- How are</i> you?
<i>- Fine. What's happend?</i>

1:07:31.173 --> 1:07:34.384
Yeah, I'm whispering
