1:07:57.908 --> 1:08:01.036
No, no!
Don't shoot me up anymore!

1:08:01.203 --> 1:08:04.623
Please! Let me see her!
I need to see her!

1:08:05.123 --> 1:08:07.375
Please, trust me.

1:08:07.542 --> 1:08:09.795
- Please.
- Trust me.

1:08:11.338 --> 1:08:13.256
Everything will be okay.

1:10:14.669 --> 1:10:17.672
What, you still think your watch
is going to show up?

1:10:17.839 --> 1:10:19.299
I left it here.

1:10:19.591 --> 1:10:22.093
We're all decent people here.

1:10:25.972 --> 1:10:28.391
It could be in the bags of dirt.

1:10:28.558 --> 1:10:34.606
Finally after 500 years a Spaniard
finally brings something to this land.

1:10:35.440 --> 1:10:37.400
What's your fucking problem,
Canario?

1:10:37.567 --> 1:10:40.237
Everything I do bothers you.

1:10:40.570 --> 1:10:43.531
Everything okay?
ls it still intact?

1:10:43.698 --> 1:10:45.075
Yeah. It hasn't moved.

1:10:45.242 --> 1:10:47.535
- Did you check the charge?
- Yeah.

1:10:48.745 --> 1:10:52.999
Don't worry. A piece of the floor
will fall, not the whole bank.

1:10:53.500 --> 1:10:54.542
Okay...

1:10:54.918 --> 1:10:57.212
We did a good job.

1:10:57.879 --> 1:11:00.674
Clear your minds,
don't say anything.

1:11:02.008 --> 1:11:04.844
- Can we get some rest?
- Yeah.

1:11:05.512 --> 1:11:07.264
We go in at 8.

1:11:25.782 --> 1:11:27.534
I'm going to lock the door, okay?

1:11:27.701 --> 1:11:29.286
I'll be right back.

1:16:19.242 --> 1:16:20.368
Do you need to check it?

1:16:21.869 --> 1:16:22.912
No.

