1:17:28.227 --> 1:17:29.771
Come on, here we go!
Let's go.

1:17:29.937 --> 1:17:30.897
Here we go!

1:18:10.061 --> 1:18:11.896
- Go on.
- Wait.

1:18:12.313 --> 1:18:13.815
Careful, you'll hit your head.

1:18:13.981 --> 1:18:15.566
Tell me if everything's okay.

1:18:16.359 --> 1:18:18.319
Go ahead.

1:18:20.530 --> 1:18:22.532
Pass me that rope.

1:18:22.699 --> 1:18:24.033
Here.

1:18:40.925 --> 1:18:42.051
Come on.

1:21:07.864 --> 1:21:09.407
Come here.

1:21:10.992 --> 1:21:13.452
Listen.
It sounds like water.

1:21:33.264 --> 1:21:35.433
There's water down there?

1:21:36.309 --> 1:21:39.145
René, can you hear me?
ls there water down there?

1:21:50.573 --> 1:21:51.782
We need to get out!

1:21:52.074 --> 1:21:53.784
Bring everything!
We have to get out!

1:22:22.396 --> 1:22:23.898
What are you doing?

1:22:24.065 --> 1:22:25.274
We're not going to make it.

1:22:25.858 --> 1:22:27.360
We're not going to make it.

1:22:29.236 --> 1:22:32.281
Canario!
I can't make it, Canario!

1:22:32.740 --> 1:22:34.158
I can't see her!

1:22:34.325 --> 1:22:36.285
Don't go down there,
it could collapse.

1:22:36.452 --> 1:22:38.663
We need to get out of here!
Come on!

1:22:48.089 --> 1:22:49.632
Canario!

1:22:50.132 --> 1:22:52.134
Canario, you bastard!

1:23:07.316 --> 1:23:09.318
Help me! Help me!

1:23:10.987 --> 1:23:12.154
Help me, you bastard!

1:23:15.741 --> 1:23:18.536
There's a guy down here!
Son of a bitch!

1:23:19.203 --> 1:23:20.788
I've got him!

1:23:21.288 --> 1:23:24.291
Help me, you bastard!
There's a guy down here!

1:23:24.458 --> 1:23:26.002
He's down here!

1:23:40.850 --> 1:23:42.893
Open up! Open UP!

1:23:43.060 --> 1:23:46.313
Open up, you son of a bitch!

1:23:46.480 --> 1:23:49.108
Open Up, Open up!

1:23:50.234 --> 1:23:51.777
Help me!

1:23:52.611 --> 1:23:54.030
Open up!

1:25:49.728 --> 1:25:51.564
We have to sound the alarm.

1:26:10.958 --> 1:26:12.459
Berta.

1:26:13.002 --> 1:26:14.295
Berta.

1:26:16.380 --> 1:26:17.965
Berta.

1:26:23.804 --> 1:26:26.849
Berta.
