1:26:50.915 --> 1:26:52.750
I don't give a shit about the money.

1:26:53.167 --> 1:26:54.460
Tell me what happened.

1:26:54.627 --> 1:26:55.961
They left.

1:26:56.962 --> 1:26:58.797
You idiot!

1:27:00.132 --> 1:27:02.718
They'll come back! And what do you
think will happen to me?

1:27:03.844 --> 1:27:05.095
I couldn't trust you.

1:27:05.262 --> 1:27:06.555
Yes, you could.

1:27:07.056 --> 1:27:08.432
You know you could.

1:27:09.099 --> 1:27:11.352
Now you're on your own.

1:27:12.728 --> 1:27:14.647
I didn't risk you two.

1:27:17.191 --> 1:27:18.776
I didn't...

1:27:23.447 --> 1:27:26.659
You don't know what it means.
I have to take care of her, Joaquin.

1:27:28.160 --> 1:27:29.495
I have to go.

1:27:29.954 --> 1:27:31.580
Let me go.

1:27:31.830 --> 1:27:33.832
I have to take care of my daughter.

1:27:36.126 --> 1:27:37.878
I can take care of you both.

1:27:39.797 --> 1:27:41.423
We can leave, the three of us.

1:27:42.675 --> 1:27:44.385
Together.

1:27:50.599 --> 1:27:52.142
I'm sorry.

1:27:54.603 --> 1:27:56.605
I really like you.

1:27:57.940 --> 1:27:58.941
