1:30:13.325 --> 1:30:14.451
Police!

1:30:19.957 --> 1:30:22.918
Good evening, sir.
Officer Cristiani.

1:30:23.085 --> 1:30:24.253
- Are you alone at home?
- No.

1:30:24.420 --> 1:30:25.879
My wife and daughter
are here.

1:30:26.296 --> 1:30:28.757
Would you mind if we came inside?

1:30:28.924 --> 1:30:32.177
Please, I was waiting
for someone to come.

1:30:32.344 --> 1:30:34.471
My whole basement is flooded.
All my work stuff.

1:30:34.638 --> 1:30:38.475
