1:33:18.302 --> 1:33:20.887
Come and shut the door.

1:33:30.147 --> 1:33:32.107
Give me your cell phone.

1:33:35.193 --> 1:33:36.945
That one right there.

1:33:53.754 --> 1:33:54.546
Here.

1:33:54.713 --> 1:33:56.923
Now you have my number.

1:33:57.215 --> 1:33:59.134
If you find anything strange

1:33:59.301 --> 1:34:01.261
or you remember anything,

1:34:01.470 --> 1:34:03.096
call me.

1:34:05.557 --> 1:34:06.767
Okay.

1:34:09.394 --> 1:34:12.981
