1:34:24.284 --> 1:34:25.786
Chief.

1:35:02.656 --> 1:35:03.865
Who is it?

1:35:04.324 --> 1:35:06.034
Police, sir.

1:35:07.744 --> 1:35:10.038
Do you mind if we come inside?

1:35:11.873 --> 1:35:15.919
The police were just here.
They already searched the house.

1:35:16.128 --> 1:35:19.464
Another brigade.
It will only be a minute.

1:35:21.383 --> 1:35:22.843
Okay.

1:35:23.301 --> 1:35:25.095
Sure, come in.

1:35:33.019 --> 1:35:35.564
That's the basement.

1:35:53.039 --> 1:35:56.209
<i>- Yeah.
- They stole the narcos box, you idiot!</i>

1:35:56.376 --> 1:35:57.753
<i>BOX 748.</i>

1:35:57.919 --> 1:36:00.297
<i>You're dead if you don't
give back that money.</i>

1:36:00.464 --> 1:36:03.300
I know these guys,
I can send them over if you want.

1:36:03.800 --> 1:36:05.427
What you're saying
is impossible.

1:36:05.844 --> 1:36:07.179
I can't talk to you right now.

1:36:07.637 --> 1:36:09.931
Give me time, I'll check it out.

1:36:10.098 --> 1:36:13.059
<i>L know you think I'll kill you
so they can't connect you to me.</i>

1:36:13.351 --> 1:36:16.396
I can't talk right now,
I'll call you back.

1:36:16.563 --> 1:36:17.481
<i>You son of a bitch.</i>

1:36:17.647 --> 1:36:19.733
Tell me where you are!

1:36:21.651 --> 1:36:22.944
What's wrong?

1:36:24.404 --> 1:36:27.073
- Nothing, go to sleep.
- You haven't eaten?

1:36:27.824 --> 1:36:30.535
Eat something sweet
or your sugar will be too low.

1:36:30.702 --> 1:36:33.246
Tell me.
What happened down there?

1:36:37.793 --> 1:36:40.629
Water started coming
from everywhere.

1:36:40.796 --> 1:36:42.839
It looks like the floor
caved in

1:36:43.006 --> 1:36:44.716
because they were making
a tunnel

1:36:44.883 --> 1:36:47.177
to rob the bank next door.

1:36:48.178 --> 1:36:51.348
At least that's what
the other policemen said.

1:36:53.725 --> 1:36:56.144
Does anyone else live here?

1:36:56.853 --> 1:36:58.396
No.

1:36:58.814 --> 1:37:00.732
No, not anymore.

1:37:01.316 --> 1:37:04.861
Until yesterday there was a girl
with her daughter,

1:37:06.071 --> 1:37:09.908
they were renting a room
upstairs with a terrace.

1:37:10.367 --> 1:37:11.326
But they left.

1:37:12.619 --> 1:37:13.829
They left?

1:37:13.995 --> 1:37:15.372
Yeah.

1:37:15.622 --> 1:37:16.915
They were...

1:37:18.792 --> 1:37:21.503
They were looking for an apartment.

1:37:22.379 --> 1:37:24.506
She said they found one.

1:37:25.257 --> 1:37:26.591
So...

1:37:32.222 --> 1:37:35.225
- Did they leave an address?
- No.

1:37:35.684 --> 1:37:36.476
No,

1:37:36.643 --> 1:37:38.353
they didn't.

1:37:38.645 --> 1:37:42.148
They said they'd be back
for their stuff.

1:37:42.315 --> 1:37:45.819
So if you need anything...

1:37:47.821 --> 1:37:49.030
Right.

1:37:50.282 --> 1:37:52.951
If I ask you for permission
to search the house,

1:37:53.118 --> 1:37:54.911
would that be okay?

1:37:56.162 --> 1:37:58.331
You're already searching
the basement.

1:37:58.498 --> 1:38:02.168
I just want to make sure
that everything's okay.

1:38:02.335 --> 1:38:03.962
The police

1:38:04.129 --> 1:38:06.548
already searched every room
in the house.

1:38:07.632 --> 1:38:08.884
Look...

1:38:09.426 --> 1:38:11.845
I think you're right,
there's no need.

1:38:14.848 --> 1:38:16.933
So the girl and her daughter
are gone?

1:38:17.100 --> 1:38:18.226
No, no.

1:38:35.368 --> 1:38:36.745
Let's go.

1:38:41.499 --> 1:38:42.667
Berta.

1:38:43.251 --> 1:38:45.295
Can you hear me?
Berta.

1:38:46.087 --> 1:38:47.505
Berta.

1:38:48.632 --> 1:38:49.633
What did you do to her?

1:38:49.799 --> 1:38:52.636
Nothing. I didn't do anything.
What's wrong with her?

1:38:59.184 --> 1:39:01.102
I think you and I need to talk.

1:39:15.492 --> 1:39:16.493
Well?

1:39:16.660 --> 1:39:19.120
It looks like the water

1:39:19.287 --> 1:39:21.122
made the floor cave in.

1:39:43.895 --> 1:39:46.773
I don't understand what's
happening, officer.

1:39:46.940 --> 1:39:48.858
Can I call you officer?

1:39:52.612 --> 1:39:54.406
Why did you say they had left?

1:39:55.657 --> 1:39:59.411
She told me to say
that they had left.

1:39:59.577 --> 1:40:01.997
And why is she drugged

1:40:02.163 --> 1:40:03.790
with marks from being tied up?

1:40:03.957 --> 1:40:06.459
Marks from being tied up?

1:40:07.335 --> 1:40:09.713
Who would have tied her up?

1:40:09.879 --> 1:40:12.674
- I have no idea.
- That's why I'm asking.

1:40:12.841 --> 1:40:13.591
I don't know.

1:40:14.467 --> 1:40:16.386
Why is she in your bed?

1:40:17.303 --> 1:40:19.222
She wasn't feeling well.

1:40:19.389 --> 1:40:23.018
She took a pill, felt dizzy,
so I said use my bed.

1:40:23.727 --> 1:40:26.354
She couldn't make it upstairs.

1:40:29.691 --> 1:40:31.943
You know this makes no sense.

1:40:32.610 --> 1:40:34.696
But I'm telling you the truth.

1:40:35.780 --> 1:40:37.991
Is the paralysis true
or is that a lie too?

1:40:38.158 --> 1:40:39.451
It's not a lie.

1:40:39.784 --> 1:40:41.828
None of it is a lie.

1:40:43.621 --> 1:40:45.749
When someone tells a lie,

1:40:47.208 --> 1:40:50.086
they have to tell at least
two more to cover it up.

1:40:50.253 --> 1:40:52.839
And then four more
to cover those two.

1:40:53.214 --> 1:40:57.969
You reach a point where
you don't even know how it started.

1:41:06.561 --> 1:41:09.355
Listen to me.

1:41:10.231 --> 1:41:11.483
Please...

1:41:23.203 --> 1:41:24.329
Listen.

1:41:24.996 --> 1:41:27.624
You'd better tell me everything
that happened here.

1:41:30.251 --> 1:41:31.878
I swear I have no idea.

1:41:32.045 --> 1:41:33.296
I have no idea, I swear.

1:41:33.463 --> 1:41:36.174
- Did you see her talk to anyone?
- No.

1:41:50.230 --> 1:41:52.398
It's important for you
to understand something.

1:41:52.565 --> 1:41:53.399
You saw our faces.

1:41:53.566 --> 1:41:55.068
We have to kill you.

1:41:55.235 --> 1:41:57.654
I don't know who you are.

1:41:57.821 --> 1:42:01.157
Right now we are death
personified for you.

1:42:01.366 --> 1:42:02.617
I don't understand.

1:42:02.784 --> 1:42:03.993
I don't understand.

1:42:12.293 --> 1:42:14.170
You only have two options.

1:42:15.380 --> 1:42:18.091
You're in a narrow corridor
with two doors.

1:42:19.008 --> 1:42:21.386
The first door is the one
you've chosen so far:

1:42:21.553 --> 1:42:24.931
Play dumb and stall
to see if that saves you.

1:42:25.431 --> 1:42:28.852
But that door leads to
the worst death

1:42:29.018 --> 1:42:32.105
you can imagine.
Extremely painful.

1:42:32.272 --> 1:42:33.773
You'll watch us hurt you,

1:42:34.315 --> 1:42:35.817
chop you to pieces,

1:42:36.943 --> 1:42:39.529
break your bones,
take out your teeth,

1:42:39.696 --> 1:42:42.991
all very slowly,
with blood everywhere.

1:42:43.700 --> 1:42:45.785
It will surprise you.

1:42:45.952 --> 1:42:50.165
How much your body
can take before you die.

1:42:51.624 --> 1:42:54.502
The second door
is the smart one.

1:42:55.086 --> 1:42:57.088
You talk, tell me
everything you know,

1:42:57.255 --> 1:42:59.465
and you die quickly,
without even realizing.

1:43:00.216 --> 1:43:04.262
It's up to you.
Which door will you choose?

1:43:07.807 --> 1:43:09.517
Put the rag on him.

1:43:09.851 --> 1:43:11.477
No, no...

1:43:11.644 --> 1:43:12.687
So you won't scream.

1:43:12.854 --> 1:43:15.481
Because you're going to,
it's impossible not to.

1:43:27.869 --> 1:43:30.038
Are you sure
you don't want to talk?

1:43:45.428 --> 1:43:46.429
Hello?

1:43:46.596 --> 1:43:49.057
<i>I'm outside your front door.</i>

1:43:53.061 --> 1:43:54.812
Come on in, motherfucker.

1:43:54.979 --> 1:43:57.732
- Help me understand this.
- What's going on?

1:43:57.941 --> 1:44:00.526
What are you doing here?
Are you crazy?

1:44:00.693 --> 1:44:04.030
- Give me back my gun!
- You've got some explaining to do.

1:44:04.239 --> 1:44:05.615
- What are you doing?
- Walk.

1:44:05.782 --> 1:44:06.824
Walk, walk.

1:44:06.991 --> 1:44:08.409
Walk.

1:44:08.576 --> 1:44:11.120
Explain. Why did you call
that cell phone?

1:44:11.287 --> 1:44:15.500
You explain to me.
I have people on the way.

1:44:15.667 --> 1:44:18.211
Explain everything to me!

1:44:20.546 --> 1:44:22.340
Listen closely.

1:44:22.507 --> 1:44:24.884
Where the hell did you get
that cell number?

1:44:25.093 --> 1:44:29.764
That guy sent me a message
saying to come.

1:44:32.433 --> 1:44:33.184
Tie him up.

1:44:33.351 --> 1:44:35.812
No, I'll stay put.
You don't have to tie me up.

1:44:35.979 --> 1:44:38.356
Listen to me.

1:44:38.523 --> 1:44:40.858
In 5 minutes there will be
cops everywhere.

1:44:41.025 --> 1:44:44.320
Yeah, right. And you come
to ring the doorbell first.

1:44:44.487 --> 1:44:45.989
You think I'm fucking stupid?

1:44:46.155 --> 1:44:50.535
Listen to me!
I don't understand this either!

1:44:50.702 --> 1:44:52.537
Don't worry, we're going
to figure it out.

1:44:52.870 --> 1:44:54.247
Look!

1:44:54.414 --> 1:44:56.791
Listen to me, you bastard.

1:44:56.958 --> 1:45:01.379
I don't understand shit here.
Explain this to me.

1:45:01.546 --> 1:45:02.922
Why did he call you?

1:45:03.089 --> 1:45:05.883
I don't know, I swear.

1:45:07.135 --> 1:45:09.345
Bring Berta out here,
she's in his room.

1:45:09.512 --> 1:45:11.723
They have two minutes to talk
or we're gone.

1:45:11.889 --> 1:45:13.766
Put her in his wheelchair.
Guttman!

1:45:14.517 --> 1:45:17.061
Watch. In one minute
you're next.

1:45:17.228 --> 1:45:18.813
No,no,no!

1:45:18.980 --> 1:45:21.941
Don't kill him!
You'll complicate everything!

1:45:22.108 --> 1:45:23.359
Stop, stop!

1:45:23.526 --> 1:45:25.528
Lefty! Lefty! Please!

1:45:25.695 --> 1:45:27.030
Don't let him kill me, Lefty!

1:45:27.196 --> 1:45:28.406
Tell him!

1:45:33.036 --> 1:45:34.746
How does he know your name?

1:45:34.912 --> 1:45:36.080
How should I know?

1:45:38.041 --> 1:45:39.500
Talk!

1:45:41.377 --> 1:45:43.338
Tell him or I will.

1:45:43.796 --> 1:45:45.465
Tell him.

1:45:46.049 --> 1:45:47.383
Please.

1:45:48.217 --> 1:45:52.722
Talk, motherfucker!
How the hell do you know him?

1:45:52.889 --> 1:45:55.266
Please, Lefty. Tell him.

1:45:55.850 --> 1:45:59.062
I have no fucking idea
what he's talking about.

1:45:59.228 --> 1:46:01.105
I don't know him.

1:46:02.065 --> 1:46:04.817
You have 3 seconds
before I blow your head off.

1:46:08.112 --> 1:46:12.575
In the evening...
he'd sneak up to the terrace.

1:46:13.576 --> 1:46:14.786
To see Berta.

1:46:16.079 --> 1:46:17.288
What?

1:46:17.455 --> 1:46:18.790
He told me about the robbery.

1:46:18.956 --> 1:46:21.376
He's making this up!

1:46:21.542 --> 1:46:23.127
Let him talk!

1:46:23.294 --> 1:46:25.463
He and Berta told me
about the robbery.

1:46:26.172 --> 1:46:28.674
About the tunnel.

1:46:28.883 --> 1:46:32.345
He said to make a hole
in my basement

1:46:32.512 --> 1:46:35.056
to grab the money
from the carts.

1:46:35.765 --> 1:46:38.601
We were going to split it
three ways.

1:46:38.768 --> 1:46:41.979
But then you changed
to cat carriers.

1:46:42.146 --> 1:46:44.023
Son of a bitch!

1:46:44.273 --> 1:46:46.442
I told you he was a son of a bitch!

1:46:46.609 --> 1:46:48.236
He's making it all up, I swear!

1:46:48.403 --> 1:46:50.696
I'm making it up?

1:46:51.239 --> 1:46:55.201
He tied up Berta.
He beat her, I don't know why.

1:46:55.410 --> 1:46:57.453
He wanted to keep her asleep.

1:46:57.620 --> 1:47:01.416
He gave me injections
to keep her drugged.

1:47:01.582 --> 1:47:04.502
He didn't trust her
and he was afraid she'd talk.

1:47:04.669 --> 1:47:07.839
You're doing her, is that it?

1:47:10.675 --> 1:47:11.592
Galereto?

1:47:13.094 --> 1:47:14.137
You're Galereto,

1:47:14.679 --> 1:47:16.139
right?

1:47:16.931 --> 1:47:19.058
And you're Canario, right?

1:47:19.350 --> 1:47:22.145
You three are going to hide
in a house in Lomas?

1:47:25.231 --> 1:47:27.108
Nobody else knew about that.

1:47:27.316 --> 1:47:29.861
I have no fucking idea
how he knows that.

1:47:30.111 --> 1:47:32.447
Shut the fuck up
and let him talk!

1:47:35.408 --> 1:47:37.702
Look, there's a key in that drawer.

1:47:38.327 --> 1:47:39.328
Open the door.

1:47:40.163 --> 1:47:41.581
You'll see I'm not lying.

1:48:08.774 --> 1:48:10.860
He left it here.

1:48:22.788 --> 1:48:23.539
Pedro, no!

1:48:24.874 --> 1:48:27.543
No,no,no!

1:48:27.710 --> 1:48:30.296
Pedro, it's okay.

1:48:30.463 --> 1:48:34.425
No,no,no!
It's okay, bro.

1:48:35.593 --> 1:48:37.720
Don't go...

1:48:39.430 --> 1:48:40.932
Don't go...

1:49:20.388 --> 1:49:21.889
Son of a bitch!

1:49:23.224 --> 1:49:24.600
Son of a bitch...

1:49:24.767 --> 1:49:27.395
Fucking bitch!
Fucking bitch!

1:49:44.120 --> 1:49:45.788
Sweetheart...

1:49:45.955 --> 1:49:49.834
I'm sorry, baby. I'm sorry.

1:49:50.001 --> 1:49:52.712
I'm sorry, I'm sorry...

1:49:55.423 --> 1:49:57.717
That's it, it's over.
That's it.

1:50:12.940 --> 1:50:14.191
You need to go.

1:50:14.775 --> 1:50:17.486
Please, get her out of here.

1:50:18.070 --> 1:50:19.572
She needs to get out of here.

1:50:20.489 --> 1:50:22.575
Stay where you are!

1:50:30.541 --> 1:50:31.876
In the end...

1:50:32.585 --> 1:50:35.713
no matter how organized
your plan is,

1:50:35.880 --> 1:50:37.882
it always depends on
either a girl or luck.

1:50:39.300 --> 1:50:41.135
Stop aiming that at me.

1:50:41.302 --> 1:50:44.180
What are you going to do,
bury 4 bodies in the basement?

1:50:46.474 --> 1:50:49.435
So you stole his girlfriend.

1:50:51.145 --> 1:50:53.564
Of course, that's my job,
you know.

1:50:56.484 --> 1:50:58.319
To know everything.

1:51:06.243 --> 1:51:09.205
Scrub the stains
with oxygenated water.

1:51:10.706 --> 1:51:12.917
That's the only thing
that gets the blood out.

1:51:15.503 --> 1:51:16.879
Okay.

1:51:18.464 --> 1:51:21.050
Where's the money you took?

1:51:23.803 --> 1:51:29.058
I take half the money,
and you think about all the things

1:51:29.225 --> 1:51:31.936
I won't do to screw up your life.

1:51:38.192 --> 1:51:39.902
I can screw up your life too.

1:51:49.537 --> 1:51:54.709
<i>These are the safety deposit boxes
you can't touch</i>

1:51:55.000 --> 1:51:58.170
<i>because they're connected
to the alarm.</i>

1:51:58.796 --> 1:52:00.381
<i>It's true that after...</i>

1:52:21.610 --> 1:52:24.989
What you've got there only saves you
for the time being.

1:52:26.490 --> 1:52:28.909
The time being, that's all.

1:52:38.252 --> 1:52:40.463
Pick which one goes first.

1:52:51.724 --> 1:52:54.226
The backpack with the money
is right there.

1:53:04.528 --> 1:53:07.239
Erase what you've got there,
trust me.

1:53:09.909 --> 1:53:12.453
Believe me, you can't afford it.

1:53:21.003 --> 1:53:22.713
In the end...

1:53:23.255 --> 1:53:25.257
Like I said before.

1:53:25.716 --> 1:53:29.887
Everything depends on a girl
or luck.
